data.description: Welcome to this 5 bed, 2.5 bath home, offering plenty of space for a large household or the perfect place to entertain. Boasting a spacious living area with a loft above as well as a bedroom and a large attic, this home lacks absolutely nothing. Recently this home was remodeled and updates include a new roof, two new HVACs, a privacy fence for the large backyard, and a full encapsulation of the crawlspace, just to name a few. It exudes so much character and southern charm complete with a wraparound porch and a cozy atmosphere. The space is endless and I promise you won't want to miss your opportunity to own this piece of Hartselle, inside the city limits and with Hartselle schools.
